---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Learn about Nivedita Mishra and the story behind Moonbeam Talent.">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="label" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">About</span>
      <h1>The Person Behind Moonbeam</h1>
      <p>12+ years of talent acquisition. 3,000+ hires. One deeply personal mission.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-hero-grid" id="about-nivedita-mishra">
        <div class="about-photo photo-frame">
          <img src="/img/pic/Nivedita5.jpg" alt="Nivedita Mishra" />
        </div>
        <div class="prose">
          <h2>About Nivedita Mishra</h2>
          <p>
            I am passionate about making a positive impact, both in people's lives and in the growth of the companies I partner with. For me, creating value and leaving a lasting impression is not just part of my work, it's part of who I am.
          </p>
          <p>
            Born and raised in India, I have spent half my life abroad and had the privilege of working across India, Canada, and Denmark. These experiences have shaped my global perspective, deepened my appreciation for cultural diversity, and strengthened my expertise in building inclusive, high-performing teams.
          </p>
          <p>
With more than 12 years in Talent Acquisition, I have led over 3,000 hires across the globe, especially in India, Denmark, Sweden, Germany, Italy, the UK, Canada, and the USA. I have partnered with companies at every stage (founding teams, scale-ups, and global enterprises), working with brands like <strong> Vivino, Neurons, Onomondo, Curity, Viebke & West, Microsoft, Amazon, Capgemini, GE Healthcare, SAS, Media.Net, Glance, Netcore, Inmobi, OYO, JoistApp, </strong> and <strong>Mosaic</strong>. This journey has given me both the reach and the insight to connect the right talent with the right opportunities.          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-alt" id="the-story-behind-moonbeam">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-layout">
        <div class="prose">
          <span class="label">Our Story</span>
          <h2>The Story Behind Moonbeam</h2>
          <p>
            In 2024, my life changed completely. I lost my mother, my greatest source of strength and guidance, and in the very same month, I lost my job at Vivino due to restructuring. Out of that moment of loss and uncertainty, Moonbeam Talent Solutions was born.
          </p>
          <p>
            The name Moonbeam comes from my mother's Indian name, <strong>Jyotsna</strong>, which means <em>moonlight</em>. Guided by her values of resilience, honesty, and respect, Moonbeam is both her legacy and my purpose. It symbolizes light, trust, and growth: the principles at the heart of everything I do.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every project I sign and every client I take on, whether it's recruitment or career consulting, if it's a 100,000 DKK engagement or a 100 DKK session, it's deeply personal and not just business. It's about creating impact, building trust, and shaping careers and teams with integrity and care.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="why-moonbeam">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="story-layout">
        <div class="prose">
          <span class="label">Why Us</span>
          <h2>Why Moonbeam?</h2>
          <p>
            Moonbeam is built on three defining values: trust, transparency, and meaningful impact, for organisations, teams, and individuals alike.
          </p>
          <p>
            Recruitment should never be reduced to a transaction. The people you hire shape growth, influence culture, and define long-term success. Meaningful hiring starts with understanding why a role exists, what success looks like, and giving hiring managers the clarity to make confident decisions.
          </p>
          <p>
            This is where Moonbeam works differently.
          </p>
          <p>
            With experience across Denmark, Europe, North America, and India, Moonbeam combines local insight with global perspective. Every search is approached with depth and intent, not just matching skills but understanding context, team dynamics, and long-term value.
          </p>
          <p>
            With a strong focus on multicultural and diversity hiring, Moonbeam helps organisations build inclusive, high-performing teams designed for sustainable growth.
          </p>
          <p>
            When you work with Moonbeam, you gain more than recruitment support. You gain a trusted partner who understands your goals and represents your brand with integrity.
          </p>
          <p>
            For professionals, Moonbeam offers career consulting that goes beyond CVs and ATS systems. By understanding your strengths and ambitions, Moonbeam helps you build meaningful connections, grow your network in Denmark, and move towards opportunities that truly fit.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-photo {
    max-width: 350px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .about-hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 350px 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .story-layout {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

</style>
